{
  "stem": "6016.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And to go to rush to be on time, not to be late, and to come back.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Once I worked the night shift, which until today, I remember very, very well.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's the worst time is our 1, 2, and 3 o'clock in the morning.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was the worst hour.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You fell asleep.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And daytime, we could visit a little, and clean up the barracks to keep it clean, to do some house chores, because there were inspections in the barracks, duties, certain duties.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And if one could have a duty in the kitchen, that was a reward.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You could have another slice of bread, or another potato, or anything.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was-- so my recollection about Neusalz was not bad.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had bunk beds, up and down.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had my sister.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think we slept with my sister together, yes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we kept warm at night--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--cuddling.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I recall very little at the barracks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember-- well, I remember the work, and that helped me to survive, and to be helpful to my sister too.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And hoping that one day we will, we will get together and, and have our parents.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But later on, it went too far.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was, it was a little less and less hope.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hope?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We never lost hope.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One day, I remember there was one French soldier who was a little, little guy.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he told us once when Rosh Hashanah comes up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was really influential, and he knew.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So he tried to help.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So it was really very, very helpful, and optimistic too.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
